sequenceDiagram
    participant Cron as Scheduler
    participant Core as Core dispatcher
    participant Dream as Dream batch
    participant Tool as Configured tool
    participant Recorder as Signal recorder
    participant Data as Data-access APIs

    Cron->>Data: load_due_entries(now)
    Data-->>Cron: due_entries
    alt use-plane entry
      Cron->>Core: dispatch(scheduled_invocation, persona_slug)
      Core->>Tool: execute(tool_name, args, env)
      Tool-->>Core: tool_result(exit_code, stdout, stderr)
      Core->>Recorder: record_signal(invocation, result, success_tags)
      Recorder->>Data: insert_signal(persona_slug, signal)
    else management entry
      Cron->>Dream: run_dream(reason=scheduled)
      Dream-->>Cron: dream_exit(status)
    end
    Cron->>Data: mark_schedule_attempt(entry_id, status)
    Note over Cron,Recorder: Only the use-plane branch records a signal.
